          The level number of this level.

          The game timer for this level. It keeps track of how much time has passed while the level is being played.

          long previousTime
          Stores how much time has passed, in milliseconds, since the level was started at the previous iteration of the game loop.

          long t
          Stores how much time has passed, in milliseconds, since the level was started.

          boolean isPaused
          Stores whether the game is currently paused.

        • sound

          Audio sound
          The Audio object for the level that controls sound playback.

        • keyPressed

          int keyPressed
          Stores the arrow key most recently pressed. The possible values are based on the DirectionHelper class. A value of -1 indicates that no arrow key is being pressed.

          Stores the current column of the matrix of rooms.
